{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775838788450,"sessionID":"ses_287c2af5affeyN4a421B18EChw","part":{"id":"prt_d783d7b32001tAJ7cdiVUkcpi5","messageID":"msg_d783d6d4b001UnqlM5ODZ7F2Sd","sessionID":"ses_287c2af5affeyN4a421B18EChw","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-4ab560b914df48e79c0063ffe2fc60ef","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n2: \n3: > Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n4: > Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n5: \n6: ## Purpose\n7: \n8: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\n9: It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\n10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n11: \n12: ## Tech Stack\n13: \n14: | Layer | Technology |\n15: |-------|-----------|\n16: | Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\n24: \n25: ## Architecture\n26: \n27: ```\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\n34:   Sandbox Pods (with optional PicoD daemon)\n35:   Agentd (idle cleanup controller)\n36:   Optional: Volcano vc-agent-scheduler\n37: ```\n38: \n39: ## Conventions\n40: \n41: - Go packages under `pkg/`, binaries under `cmd/`\n42: - Python CLI at `cmd/cli/`, SDK at `sdk-python/`\n43: - JSON tags use camelCase; Go structs use PascalCase\n44: - K8s resources use `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` API group\n45: - Normative language: SHALL = mandatory, SHOULD = recommended, MAY = optional\n\n(End of file - total 45 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n\n> Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n> Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n\n## Purpose\n\nAgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\nIt provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\nsession-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n| Layer | Technology |\n|-------|-----------|\n| Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n| Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n| HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n| Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n| Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md","time":{"start":1775838788439,"end":1775838788448}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775838788453,"sessionID":"ses_287c2af5affeyN4a421B18EChw","part":{"id":"prt_d783d76c4001fMBG8k3CPgmZFV","messageID":"msg_d783d6d4b001UnqlM5ODZ7F2Sd","sessionID":"ses_287c2af5affeyN4a421B18EChw","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-3dc46e7b283943b590fb57f87fa4266f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Specification\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: [To be filled during spec definition]\n5: \n6: ## Requirements\n7: [To be filled during spec definition]\n\n(End of file - total 7 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Specification\n\n## Purpose\n[To be filled during spec definition]\n\n## Requirements\n[To be filled during spec definition]","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md","time":{"start":1775838788433,"end":1775838788451}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775838788456,"sessionID":"ses_287c2af5affeyN4a421B18EChw","part":{"id":"prt_d783d7922001B2tpLLDzl87mw2","messageID":"msg_d783d6d4b001UnqlM5ODZ7F2Sd","sessionID":"ses_287c2af5affeyN4a421B18EChw","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-b848bc88d7d642d7b29ffabb5114c53e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-001/README.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-001/README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001 Implementation Notes\n2: \n3: ## Implementation Status\n4: - [ ] Spec definition\n5: - [ ] Go type definitions\n6: - [ ] CRD registration\n7: - [ ] Tests\n8: - [ ] Documentation\n9: \n10: ## Notes\n11: [Implementation notes to be added during development]\n\n(End of file - total 11 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 Implementation Notes\n\n## Implementation Status\n- [ ] Spec definition\n- [ ] Go type definitions\n- [ ] CRD registration\n- [ ] Tests\n- [ ] Documentation\n\n## Notes\n[Implementation notes to be added during development]","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-001/README.md","time":{"start":1775838788437,"end":1775838788454}}}}
